p4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 stages of Aether-flavored microgames!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go for high scores in endless modes of every stage!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new original soundtrack directed by flashygoodness!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A smattering of unique artstyles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Laugh at the funny animals interacting! please</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THE LORE</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Absa! She's in this one! It's not a fakeout!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dan Fornace-approved, i think?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3463050/extras/c87f63671465f7d15e09b4ad6645f738.poster.avif?t=1743527778\" width=478 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3463050/extras/c87f63671465f7d15e09b4ad6645f738.webm?t=1743527778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
